{"tid":2079651,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新疆和田6.4級地震 震央附近暫無傷亡及損毀報告","createTime":"2020-06-26T02:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T02:38:46.000Z","uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"506fc730fcea35a6a964f610e70b17be1ea999a2","tid":2079651,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"新疆和田地區發生6.4級地震，于田縣城震感不明顯，電力、交通及通信正常，距離震央最近的鄉鎮阿羌鄉，暫時無傷亡和房屋損毀報告。中國地震台網測定，今天清晨5時05分在新疆和田地區于田縣發生6.4級地震，震源深度10公里，屬淺層地震。本港天文台亦錄得這次地震，震央位於和田東南約270公里。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-26 10:18:23<br />\n<br />\nSource: RTHK"},{"pid":"8d03aa44ed52b1a8450cf81428c9ea59e0e6ca9b","tid":2079651,"uid":129348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqFyLNF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqFyLNF.jpg&h=2eee641c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AX6evek.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAX6evek.jpg&h=60346204&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFC5BUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFC5BUk.jpg&h=9372a4fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書"},{"pid":"16aec981516914e00f85ab73fd7a0a93b5718809","tid":2079651,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"無事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e5e4e28773f87283d6d01eca473bcc8d45a6f3","tid":2079651,"uid":298114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"三峽果頭唔好地震呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e952cbf1873c2d53e39e5b10aa271b9e935c8fc6","tid":2079651,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:38